The concept of Monarchy and the queen being the head of the Church of England representing the same sort of idea as the Pope being directly connected to God.

The loss of this spiritual appointment and the role being watered down over time as even the Royal Family loses sight of all of this, but ironically they grow further from this model the more they try to grasp it because they become more concerned with their own idea of what correct behavior is based on tradition and culture.

The United States breaking free from this as people began to see that the King had become so corrupt and the furthest thing away from God as you could possibly get and trying to recreate this in a way that was better protected from the possibility of human error again.
